    dc:description "Fig. 14. Zeadalmodes myrmecophilus, male. A) Tergite VIII, B) Sternite VIII, C) Tergite IX (two lateral plates) and sternite IX (middle plate), D) Genitalia, ventral view, E) Genitalia, lateral view. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
